  "system": {
    "description": "<p><span style=\"color:rgb(239, 230, 216);font-family:Signika, 'Palatino Linotype', sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgba(12, 12, 12, 0.9);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial;display:inline !important;float:none\">A retaliation attack.</span><br />Triggers a vs Test of Dexterity against target's Strength/Dexterity Test. On attacker's success, the target is pushed 1 hex.<br />At a MoS of 25 or higher, deals 3d4 damage that ignores Armor.<br /><br />Can be performed after a successful Defense.</p>",
